sec on-yellow user_login_link" href="/login">Log in</a></li></ul><ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-center navbar-main"><li class="active"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a></li><li><a class="nav-link" href="/jobs">Jobs</a></li><li><a class="nav-link" href="/trainings/courses/latest">Courses</a></li><li><a class="nav-link" href="/discussions/articles">Forum</a></li><li><a class="nav-link" href="/hot"><span class="hidden-xs">Hot now!</span><span class="visible-xs">Hot!</span></a></li></ul><div class="clearfix"></div></div></div></div></header><section><div><div class="guest-container "><div class="row flash-msg-container"><div class="col-sm-12"></div></div><section class="jobseeker-top"><div class="section-guest banner-guest-jobseeker"><div class="container"><div class="row text-center"><div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2"><h1 class="main-title--guest">Be part of Africa&#39;s fastest growing career community</h1><div class="line-break-sm"></div><p>More than 2,000,000 people have used Fuzu to date. Get access to job recommendations, learning and career guidance â€“ for everyone from entry level to executives.</p></div><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="line-break-lg"></div><div class="state-buttons"><div class="state-buttons--full-mobile"><a class="btn-main" href="/pro/register?g=%2Fgetting-to-know-you">Join now</a></div></div><div class="line-break-sm"></div><div class="visible-xs"><img style="display:inline-block;max-height:25px;margin-right:10px;" alt="Mobile Friendly" src="/assets/mobile_friendly-02e81f618ee2b5e34001cb80d6e59bc36ad26927a7c93b73ea5926ad81cb0f01.png" /><img style="display:inline-block;margin-left:10px;max-height:25px;" alt="Free Basics" src="/assets/free_basics-dc7351c3cec4aa1a9d07768d682ba351e6afdc4baaa90e0ce218de1183b8d054.png" /></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="landing-section landing-section-darker"><div class="container auto-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-6 col-xs-offset-3 col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-3 col-md-offset-3"><img class="section-what-img" src="/assets/guest-vertical_phone-5377f6b9a145c491852ae723ade1a4e9f92d349c9667e81809306fb818a5bec7.png" alt="Guest vertical phone" /></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4"><h2>What can you do on Fuzu?</h2><div class="section-question-title">Thousands of Jobs Matched to You</div><p>Quickly apply for jobs that are recommended to you based on your interests, experience, skills and career goals.</p><div class="section-question-title">Hundreds of Free Online Courses</div><p>Learn and build skills by accessing our free online courses.</p><div class="section-question-title">Build Your Career</div><p>Plan your next career step, be it your first job or your next big move.</p><div class="section-question-title">Fresh Daily Updates</div><p>Stay up-to-date with fresh blog posts, news and lively discussions every day.</p><div class="state-buttons"><div class="state-buttons--full-mobile"><a class="btn-main" href="/pro/register?g=%2Fgetting-to-know-you">Take me to Fuzu</a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="landing-section"><div class="container auto-container"><section class="section-guest"><div class="company-and-media text-center"><h2>Now hiring on Fuzu</h2><div class="line-break-sm"></div><ul class="logo-table"><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/m-kopa-kenya-ltd"><img class="grayscaled" alt="M-KOPA SOLAR" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_a1385cef-4f41-49bd-af37-ffdd2a3fee34.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/equity-bank-kenya"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Equity Bank Kenya " data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_4de639d3-2e7a-430b-91f0-a46ef64d3c18.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/yusudi"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Yusudi" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_18ad19d0-cfe9-4360-9bad-2c4aa454b156.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/jubilee-insurance-ke"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Jubilee Insurance KE" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_4f6a2e6e-6b59-4082-83c0-8f048dafaa7b.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/microsoft"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Microsoft 4Afrika Skills" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_bf00c2a9-1ec0-4cc0-9093-f82f102acdff.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/securex-agencies-k-ltd"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Securex Agencies (K) LTD" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_d4a7e387-9729-4e3c-95f0-4018d49dac0d.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/infectious-diseases-research-collaboration"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Infectious Diseases Research Collaboration" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_01be0dfa-1a39-4e05-b26f-a5540f8d52db.png" src="" /></a></li><li class="logo-container"><a href="/company/bagda-s-auto-spares-limited"><img class="grayscaled" alt="Bagda&#39;s Auto Spares Limited" data-lazy="https://s3.amazonaws.com/fuzu.com-carrierwave/employers/medium_818b9056-209b-49a3-a744-a99a6d9b50bd.jpeg" src="" /></a></li></ul><div class="clearfix"></div></div></section></div></section><section class="landing-section landing-section-colorful"><div class="container auto-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-4 col-md-offset-2"><h2>How are we different?</h2><div class="section-question-title">Fuzu is Much More Than a Job Board</div><p>Job boards are tiring! Fuzu offers you career planning tools, learning opportunities, discussions and much more to help you to progress in your life.</p><div class="section-question-title">Personal Career Advice</div><p>We offer personal career advice every step of the way and provide access to professional coaches an